Installation
1.React Package install through vite(fast installation):
Run ‘npm create vite@latest’
Provide Project_name and then Select React and Typescript/Javascript from the options.
Change the folder to the project folder and Run ‘npm install’

2.Tailwind CSS
npm create vite@latest my-project -- --template react
  cd my-project
npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer
npx tailwindcss init -p
Add the paths to all of your template files in your tailwind.config.js file.

     /** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config} */
export default {
  content: [
    "./index.html",
    "./src/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx}",
  ],
  theme: {
    extend: {},
  },
  plugins: [],
}

 Add the Tailwind directives to your CSS
                   @tailwind base;
        @tailwind components; 
        @tailwind utilities;

npm run dev

								
